                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150111-8-off41 t18150111-8-cd42"></join>, a gelding, value 30 l.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18150111-8-victim109" type="victimName">
