                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150111-8-defend107 t18150111-8-punish47"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 20.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex jury, before Mr. Justice Dallas.</p>
